---
alwaysApply: true
---

Use React + Next.js + TypeScript + shadcn/ui
Design clean, modern UI and prefer existing shadcn components.

Follow feature-based architecture:
src/features/<feature>/{components,hooks,services,types,utils,index.ts}

Rules:

- Keep code clean, modular, and maintainable
- Split UI into small reusable components
- Separate business logic from presentation
- Prefer shared components before creating new ones
- Use clear naming, strong typing, and single responsibility
- Keep files cohesive and avoid duplication

- [write docs in /docs folder, create visualize for this docs](./visual-docs.md)
